liveBlogPostPrepared.title: France vs Jamaica is underway!

children.content: The last game of a big day.

liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: Not a complete performance from the Netherlands, who were really on top in the first half. Just the one goal, a towering header from Stefanie van der Gragt from a corner in the 13th minute. Portugal came out with much more intent in the second half, but didn't really create too many clear chances. Overall a pretty formidable performance from the Dutch, even though they faded a bit in the second half.
liveBlogPostPrepared.title: FULL-TIME: Netherlands 1 - 0 Portugal

children.content: Not a complete performance from the Netherlands, who were really on top in the first half. Just the one goal, a towering header from
Stefanie van der Gragt from a corner in the 13th minute.
Portugal came out with much more intent in the second half, but didn't really create too many clear chances.
Overall a pretty formidable performance from the Dutch, even though they faded a bit in the second half.

liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: I know it's only 1-0 but the Dutch ran rings around Portugal in that first half. No shots on target from the Iberians, and Netherlands could have had two or three more goals. Formidable display from them. Portugal will have to find some inspiration in the second half if they're to turn this around.
liveBlogPostPrepared.title: HALF-TIME: Netherlands 1 - 0 Portugal

children.content: I know it's only 1-0 but the Dutch ran rings around Portugal in that first half. No shots on target from the Iberians, and Netherlands could have had two or three more goals. Formidable display from them.
Portugal will have to find some inspiration in the second half if they're to turn this around.
